#~ "This package contains a framework for testing other programs.  It is only "
#~ "installed in the temporary toolchain."
#~ msgstr "这个软件包包含一个测试其他程序的框架。它只安装在临时工具链中。"

#~ msgid "Gcc"
#~ msgstr "Gcc"

#, fuzzy
